metadata.name: Vibes
metadata.description:
Vibes is a feel good song all around!

I dedicate this song to my niece, Taelour M. Adkins who passed away at sixteen years old. She was a beacon of light, crazy talented, and always brought amazing vibes.

Taelour, may you continue to rest in eternal peace and be a constant reminder to myself and others to live fully. I love you! #Sweet16

*15% of all proceeds will be donated to BeyondType1 in honor of Taelour M. Adkins.*
